  "changelogHtml": "<h3 id=\"compose-1.0.0-alpha02\" data-text=\"Version 1.0.0-alpha02\" tabindex=\"-1\">Version 1.0.0-alpha02</h3>\n<p>November 11, 2020</p>\n<p><code translate=\"no\" dir=\"ltr\">androidx.paging:paging-compose:1.0.0-alpha02</code> is released. <a href=\"https://android.googlesource.com/platform/frameworks/support/+log/234e23e470a5e7f81291f6acd12d538146dc010b..2d49f9fa892a0d067580a871f3aa0cd6764f4c3b/paging/compose\">Version 1.0.0-alpha02 contains these commits.</a></p>\n<p><strong>API Changes</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Added <code translate=\"no\" dir=\"ltr\">.peek()</code>, <code translate=\"no\" dir=\"ltr\">.snapshot()</code>, <code translate=\"no\" dir=\"ltr\">.retry()</code> and <code translate=\"no\" dir=\"ltr\">.refresh()</code> methods to\n<code translate=\"no\" dir=\"ltr\">LazyPagingItem</code>s which expose the same functionality available in\n<code translate=\"no\" dir=\"ltr\">AsyncPagingDataDiffer</code> / <code translate=\"no\" dir=\"ltr\">PagingDataAdapter</code> (<a href=\"https://android-review.googlesource.com/#/q/Iddfe8a8dc9339bf4aff86f562b94eabdf8f92056\">Iddfe8</a>, <a href=\"https://issuetracker.google.com/issues/172041660\">b/172041660</a>)</li>\n</ul>",
  "commitsUrl": "https://android.googlesource.com/platform/frameworks/support/+log/234e23e470a5e7f81291f6acd12d538146dc010b..2d49f9fa892a0d067580a871f3aa0cd6764f4c3b/paging/compose"
}